Once upon a time in a forest , there lived a monkey who recided on a berry tree which was on the bank of a river .
So in the same forest , there lived a crocodile and his wife .
So one day , the crocodile came to the banks of the river , and rested under the tree . 
The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits . The next day , crocodile came for more fruits . 
The crocodile and monkey became good friends .